Package keypair

Interface Summary
IKeyPairCodec The visible methods of an object that knows how to encode and decode cryptographic asymmetric keypairs.
Registry A placeholder for names and literals used throughout this library.
 

Class Summary
EncodeDecode Encode/decode public/private keys.
EncryptDecrypt RSA cryptosystem.
GenerateKeys Generates public & private keys according to bitsize.
GenerateUserKeys Generates keys based on the user input.
LoadSaveKey  
MillerRabinPrimalityTest Randomly selects numbers of defined size until a prime is found.
OpenSave Save/load public/private key to/from the file.
RsaKey A base asbtract class for both public and private RSA keys.
RsaKeyPairRawCodec An object that implements the IKeyPairCodec interface for the Raw format to use with RSA keypairs.
RsaPrivateKey An object that embodies an RSA private key.
RsaPublicKey An object that encapsulates an RSA public key.
TestPrimality Tests if a number is a prime.
